1 INTRODUCTION OF  BLOCKCHAIN TECHNOLOGY
  1. 20th century Industrial Revolution 
  2. It is a decentralized digital ledger that records transactions  securely and transparently which is  immutable

2  HOW WEB 3.0 WORKS? 
	Web 3.0 is the next evolution of the internet,focused on decentralization and users ownership
	Uses Blockchain instead of  centralized servers
	Applications run as dApps
	Users control their data via wallets

3  GOVERNMENT INVOLVEMENT IN WEB 3.0
	Government is using centralized exchange technology
	Implementing blockchain in governance
	Monitoring financial crime
	Promoting digital identity systems

